'''NGC 1475''' 是[[波江座|波江座]]的遙遠[[椭圆星系|椭圆星系]]，1886年由美國天文學家[[法蘭斯·萊文沃思|法蘭斯·萊文沃思]]發現，[[NGC天體表|天體新總表]]（{{lang|en|NGC}}）有收錄。<ref>{{cite web|first = Courtney|last = Seligman|url = http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc14a.htm#1475|title = Celestial Atlas NGC Objects: NGC 1450 - 1499|website = cseligman.com|access-date = 2022-03-22|archive-date = 2016-10-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161029235739/http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc14a.htm#1475}}</ref>

其[[面亮度|面亮度]]僅14.29 [[视星等|mag]]/[[弧分|am]]<sup>2</sup>，屬於[[低表面亮度星系|低表面亮度星系]]（LSB星系），即比鄰域[[夜空|夜空]]更暗一等的瀰漫星系。

科學家利用[[紅移|紅移]]以外的方法，測得NGC 1475距地球1.37億[[秒差距|秒差距]]<ref>{{cite web|title = Your NED Search Results|url = http://ned.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/objsearch?objname=NGC+1475&extend=no&hconst=73&omegam=0.27&omegav=0.73&corr_z=1&out_csys=Equatorial&out_equinox=J2000.0&obj_sort=RA+or+Longitude&of=pre_text&zv_breaker=30000.0&list_limit=5&img_stamp=YES#NR_Distances_0|website = ned.ipac.caltech.edu|access-date = 2016-10-31|archive-date = 2019-03-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190306044035/http://ned.ipac.caltech.edu/cgi-bin/objsearch?objname=NGC+1475&extend=no&hconst=73&omegam=0.27&omegav=0.73&corr_z=1&out_csys=Equatorial&out_equinox=J2000.0&obj_sort=RA+or+Longitude&of=pre_text&zv_breaker=30000.0&list_limit=5&img_stamp=YES#NR_Distances_0}}</ref>，與使用紅移推算的結果相符{{註|1=據[[哈勃定律|哈勃定律]]，星系離地球而去的速率為''v'' = ''H<sub>o</sub>d''，其中''H<sub>o</sub>''為[[哈勃常數|哈勃常數]]（70±5 (km/s)/Mpc），''d''為星系至地球的距離。}}。

